Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

Alembic will:
- Detect all changes in your models
- Create versions for each change you make
- Apply versions in order, updating or downgrading the database schema

To create a migration:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"

To apply migrations:
    alembic upgrade head

To rollback one migration:
    alembic downgrade -1

